description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/1753/documentation

;;Sugar refinery construction is used as a proxy for this process. This datasets presents infrastructure of vegetable oil refinery, which transforms vegetable oil, crude to vegetable oil, refined.;This dataset is approximated from the dataset 'sugar refinery construction'. It is not recommended for use if the impact of this dataset is significantly high.

This process includes land use and occupation, buildings and facilities of a what is considered to be a typical vegetable oil refinery. Energy use for construction and related emissions and/or waste effluents is not included.
category: F:Construction/42:Civil engineering/429:Construction of other civil engineering projects/4290:Construction of other civil engineering projects

processDocumentation.technologyDescription: Vegetable oils refinary consists of usually an administration building, storage halls, tanks, filters, heat exchangers and other metal or concrete structures.
processDocumentation.dataTreatmentDescription: The dataset is extrapolated from 'sugar refinery construction'.
